			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Has anybody else tried this?  I found a program which basically lets you do auto-fire archery without a gamepad.  I got it running and now I can toggle auto-fire archery on and off with F11.  It renders the Gamepad totally useless.
<br />

<br />
You can download it here:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.eqhunter.com/Files/Autofire_v0.3.zip" target="_blank">http://www.eqhunter.com/Files/Autofire_v0.3.zip</a>
<br />

<br />
Does anybody know if this is legal or not?  I've heard that any macro like this is legal as long as it can't be abused by users who are away from the keyboard, so I'd guess that this would fall under the same category as using a Gamepad.  Can anybody confirm this?<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://cabilis.net/Raingesignaturesharp.GIF" border="0" />
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=743326" target="_blank" class="postlink">Veteran Raine I'Ngoroth</a> - 65 Forest Stalker of Tholuxe Paells
