				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I tried this for 1 mob. It does work.... however I couldn't get the darn thing to turn off (was an error on my part I think but not sure). Haven't used it since because it IS third party software.
<br />

<br />
Not sure about if this falls into the same line as the gamepads because they also use software to make the autofire work. I will wait until there is more light on this subject before I use it again. There is a notice on EQHunter saying to USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. If I get the green light from a GM, I will continue to use it.... otherwise I won't. (I know a GM personally who is on vacation right now.... when he gets back to Germany I will ask him... he won't notify anyone about it if it is not legal... he's cool)
